#2.4.0
	- Implemented Text property on ComboBox

#2.3.0
	- Feature to Snap window to desktop. Implemented on Window.SnapToDesktop()

#2.2.2 Bug fix release
	- Fixed VerticalScroll bar issue, where ListViewRow couldn't be located since scroll bar only tried to scroll large. 
	  The row were then never found.
	
